instruction: Create a web page to display a portfolio.
output: A web page to display a portfolio needs several elements. The page should have a brief introduction of who made the portfolio, a list of the portfolio items, including details on each item such as project name, media type, technologies used, and live links to the items. A brief description of the portfolio and its purpose should also be included. The page should also feature a contact form to send a message to the portfolio owner.
